name: hadoop.security.groups.cache.warn.after.ms
description:
If looking up a single user to group takes longer than this amount of
    milliseconds, we will log a warning message.

name: hadoop.zk.num-retries
description: Number of tries to connect to ZooKeeper.

name: dfs.namenode.retrycache.expirytime.millis
description: The time for which retry cache entries are retained.

name: yarn.app.mapreduce.am.containerlauncher.threadpool-initial-size
description:
The initial size of thread pool to launch containers in the
    app master.

name: mapreduce.job.maxtaskfailures.per.tracker
description:
The number of task-failures on a node manager of a given job
               after which new tasks of that job aren't assigned to it. It
               MUST be less than mapreduce.map.maxattempts and
               mapreduce.reduce.maxattempts otherwise the failed task will
               never be tried on a different node.

name: fs.ftp.host.port
description: FTP filesystem connects to fs.ftp.host on this port
